data.description: Welcome to Asheville! Come make this home yours! This Quiet breathtaking neighborhood offers so much! 4 bed/3 bath home with bonus room/office! Enjoy entertaining in your open concept kitchen along large island. Cozy up to fireplace in large living area. Home has many updates. Tile floors throughout kitchen and living. Brand new Water heater and HVAC System fully replaced last year. Large Backyard with extended patio! Enjoy the neighborhood sitting on your front porch! 3 car garage provides plenty of room and storage. Neighborhood has community pool, clubhouse, dog park, playground, ball field, and basketball courts. Amenities galore. Hurry and make this home yours!
